title: CIP-F 1: Issue Founding Citizen NFTs to Dev Team
body:
**Two members of the dev team, GregR and Odyslam, have both spent over 100 hours without compensation to build CityDAO products. The core team proposes acknowledging their contributions with Founding Citizen NFTs.**

*This will increase the supply of Founding Citizen NFTs from 50 to 52.*

**GregR**
Built CityDAO parcel viewer product that will be used for first land parcel drop, including web3 for connecting wallet and buying parcels.
See his work: GitHub - citydaoproject/app: A web app to view CityDAO land parcels 2

**Odyslam**
Built smart contracts for our own in house Citizen NFTs after Opensea delisted our collection, wrote logic to manage exchanging those and manage issuing those NFTs.
See his work: GitHub - citydaoproject/citydao-citizens: ERC721 NFTs for CityDAO 1

**How issuance will work:**

First, the proposal needs to pass, then…
Core team most vote YES on successful completion of Citizen NFT project and CityDAO parcel project
NFTs can be issued on Dec 9th or later
choices: No, Do not mint more NFTs
